					<Property Name="Text">

AIM OF THE GAME:

Destroy as many enemy tanks as possible to win the game!


WEAPONS AND SKILLS

You can select the armament of your tank in the equipment menu. Equip
your tank with the weapons and skills that best fit your playing
style! Changes you make here will take effect only after your next
respawn.


SCORING

The score table shows each player's score, kills, deaths, level and
ping. Your accuracy and efficiency are displayed as well. For each
kill you are awarded two upgraded points, substantially weaker or
stronger opponents give one or four upgrade points, respectively.


UPGRADES

During the game it is possible to upgrade the tank in the three
categories weapon, armor and speed. Each category has three levels
that can be unlocked consecutively by spending upgrade points. Upgrade
points are earned by killing opponents, or helping somebody else kill
an opponent.

The upgrade menu shows a short description of each upgrade, together
with upgrade costs that need to be spent to activate an
upgrade. Upgrades can also be activated via hotkeys. Choose your
upgrades wisely to gain an advantage over your enemies!


					</Property>					
